思路比较简单，bfs，不断替换每一位，判断是不是质数并且没有搜过，是的话就加入队列，直到找到解。
~~（不用那个质数表会超时但是懒得剪枝了）~~

//质数表

bool prime(unsigned int num){//判断质数，就是这个函数生成的上面的质数表
    
    if(num<=1)return false;
    if(num==2)return true ;
    for(unsigned int i=2;i<=sqrt(num);i++)if(num%i==0)return false;
    return true;
}

bool book[10001]={0};//判断搜没搜过

unsigned int rep(unsigned int src,unsigned int index,unsigned char num){//替换某个数的某一位，从0开始
    unsigned int ctr=1;
    for(unsigned int i=0;i<index;i++)ctr*=10;
    unsigned int bef=src%ctr;
    return (src/(ctr*10)*10+num)*ctr+bef;
}

struct unum_step{unsigned int num;unsigned int step;};

unum_step bfs(unsigned int st,unsigned int fe){//暴力搜索
    
    queue<unum_step> sq; sq.push({st,0});
    
    while(!sq.empty()){
        
        unum_step now = sq.front();   sq.pop();
        
        book[now.num]=true;
        
        if(now.num==fe)return {1,now.step};
        
        for(unsigned int index=0;index<4;index++){
            for(unsigned char n=0;n<10;n++){
                unsigned int nnum = rep(now.num,index,n);
                if((!Prime[nnum])||(book[nnum]==true)||(nnum<1000)||(nnum>=10000))continue;
                else sq.push({nnum,now.step+1});
            }
        }
        
    }
    
    return {0,0};
    
}

int main(int argc , char **argv){
    
    unsigned int n;  cin>>n;
    
    while(n--){
        
        memset(book,0,10001);
        
        unsigned int a,b;    cin>>a>>b;
        
        unum_step sol = bfs(a,b);
        
        if(sol.num){
            cout<<sol.step<<endl;
        }else{
            cout<<"Impossible"<<endl;
        }
        
    }
    
    
    return 0;
    
}
